{"tid":891772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴結川普千金 中國初步批准伊凡卡16個品牌商標","createTime":"2018-11-06T11:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T11:34:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8bed1843b099450892ad4b8f510331c2b035c5b3","tid":891772,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2018/11/06/phpmfQxUX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F11%2F06%2FphpmfQxUX.jpg&h=105311b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國公民責任與道德機構調查，中國當局10月通過了伊凡卡旗下品牌16個新商標的初步批准，其中還包括了投票機商標。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕中國再度透過美國總統川普的女兒，伊凡卡‧川普（Ivanka Trump）在貿易戰上釋出善意？據美國公民責任與道德（Citizens for Responsibility and Ethics）機構調查，中國當局上個月通過了伊凡卡旗下品牌的16個新商標的初步批准，其中還包括了投票機商標。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，美國公民責任與道德機構5日公佈對中國商標的調查，指出中國當局在上月通過了美國總統川普的女兒伊凡卡旗下，16個包括時尚品牌在內的商標初步批准。該機構指出，這是中國在川普上任後，首次在單月內大量通過伊凡卡旗下公司的商標。<br />\n<br />\n據中國國家工商行政管理總​​局商標局紀錄，中國最新通過的伊凡卡旗下公司商標，包含鞋子、珠寶等品牌，另有投票機、療養院等其他商品。這些商標則從2016年開始申請批准。<br />\n<br />\n知識產權律師表示，商標申請通過後，可以為申請人提供全面的品牌保護。中國政府日前曾表示，批准伊凡卡公司的商標沒有任何不妥之處。而中國則曾在美國制裁中興事件期間，批准通過了伊凡卡旗下公司的8個商標。<br />\n<br />\n外界預期，美、中雙方將在11月的G20峰會上，商討處理貿易衝突的協議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2603862\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2603862&d=eZABLEumFf0ENTzQUFj9EE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e0d3fb76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2603862&h=9e16085b\" target=\"_blank\">http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2603862</a>"},{"pid":"31eb0fd6d91df78238780f3eb7fd3dab2d31404c","tid":891772,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:30:22.000Z","msg":"Too late"},{"pid":"185325798e837da3dfbbef20906f93f6acb3e4e5","tid":891772,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:31:55.000Z","msg":"左膠報表示   比你註冊係「巴結」"},{"pid":"af27bb08d30d0a3d2cb40224072be40b4f4abaee","tid":891772,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到無印、new Balance 雞毛鴨血<br />\n想用個伊凡卡講數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a759303d340cf2c889fda0eee450e7ae1b13bf69","tid":891772,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:33:38.000Z","msg":"大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade1371b121e59d13d72ec53a76654ef8c257975","tid":891772,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"185325798e837da3dfbbef20906f93f6acb3e4e5","tid":891772,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:31:55.000Z","msg":"左膠報表示   比你註冊係「巴結」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:34:15.000Z","msg":"又係路透射<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}